# 7-Tier Routing Algorithm
## Gateway Routing Decision Tree

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    START[📩 Receive Message<br/>channel: ${channelId}<br/>account: ${accountId}<br/>peer: ${peer.id}] --> TIER1

    subgraph TIER1[" Tier 1: binding.peer<br/>(Exact match)"]
        T1{binding.peer<br/>== peer.id?}
        T1 -- Yes --> R1[Route to<br/>agent: {agentId}<br/>📝 matched by: "peer"]
    end

    T1 -- No --> TIER2
    subgraph TIER2[" Tier 2: binding.peer.parent<br/>(Thread parent)"]
        T2{peer.parent<br/>exists?<br/>AND match?}
        T2 -- Yes --> R2[Route to<br/>agent: {agentId}<br/>📝 matched by: "peer.parent"]
    end

    T2 -- No --> TIER3
    subgraph TIER3[" Tier 3: guild + roles<br/>(Discord server + role)"]
        T3{guild match?<br/>AND roles in<br/>{roles}?}
        T3 -- Yes --> R3[Route to<br/>agent: {agentId}<br/>📝 matched by: "guild+roles"]
    end

    T3 -- No --> TIER4
    subgraph TIER4[" Tier 4: binding.guild<br/>(Any role in guild)"]
        T4{guild match?}
        T4 -- Yes --> R4[Route to<br/>agent: {agentId}<br/>📝 matched by: "guild"]
    end

    T4 -- No --> TIER5
    subgraph TIER5[" Tier 5: binding.team<br/>(Workspace level)"]
        T5{team match?<br/>(Slack workspace)}
        T5 -- Yes --> R5[Route to<br/>agent: {agentId}<br/>📝 matched by: "team"]
    end

    T5 -- No --> TIER6
    subgraph TIER6[" Tier 6: binding.account<br/>(Account-wide)"]
        T6{accountId<br/>match?}
        T6 -- Yes --> R6[Route to<br/>agent: {agentId}<br/>📝 matched by: "account"]
    end

    T6 -- No --> DEFAULT
    subgraph DEFAULT[" Tier 7 (Last Resort)"]
        DEF[Route to<br/>agent: "main"<br/>📝 matched by: "default"]
    end

    R1 & R2 & R3 & R4 & R5 & R6 --> END[✅ Agent Resolved<br/>Proceed to dispatch]
    DEF --> END

    %% Styling
    style START fill:#bbdefb,stroke:#2196f3,stroke-width:2px
    style END fill:#c8e6c9,stroke:#4caf50,stroke-width:3px
    style DEFAULT fill:#ffcdd2,stroke:#f44336,stroke-width:2px
    style R1 fill:#fff9c4,stroke:#ffeb3b
    style R2 fill:#fff9c4,stroke:#ffeb3b
    style R3 fill:#fff9c4,stroke:#ffeb3b
    style R4 fill:#fff9c4,stroke:#ffeb3b
    style R5 fill:#fff9c4,stroke:#ffeb3b
    style R6 fill:#fff9c4,stroke:#ffeb3b

    classDef tier fill:#e1bee7,stroke:#8e24aa,stroke-width:1px
    class TIER1,TIER2,TIER3,TIER4,TIER5,TIER6 tier
```

**Configuration Example:**

```json
{
  "agentBindings": [
    {
      "agentId": "vip-support",
      "peer": "123456789",                    // Tier 1
      "description": "VIP customers via direct message"
    },
    {
      "agentId": "moderator-bot",
      "guild": "987654321",
      "roles": ["admin", "moderator"],       // Tier 3
      "description": "Admin/moderator in Discord server"
    },
    {
      "agentId": "team-bot",
      "team": "T12345",                       // Tier 5
      "description": "Slack workspace assistant"
    },
    {
      "agentId": "personal-assistant",
      "account": "U99999"                     // Tier 6
    }
  ]
}
```

**Real-World Scenarios:**

| Messaging Platform | Peer ID | Guild | Team | Binding Hit |
|-------------------|---------|-------|------|-------------|
| Telegram DM | `u123456` | - | - | Tier 6 (account) or Default |
| Telegram Group | `c-987654` | - | - | Tier 6 (account) or Default |
| Discord Channel | `c123:text` | `987654321` | - | Tier 4 (guild) or Tier 3 (guild+roles) |
| Slack Channel | `C12345` | - | `T67890` | Tier 5 (team) |
| Thread reply | `t789` (parent `p456`) | - | - | Tier 2 (peer.parent) |

